    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Operations on arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "1804f174"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "f563ce67",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.transpose(data)"
      ],
      "id": "ebcf4533",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "c835d831"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.random.randn(1, 2, 3, 4, 5)"
      ],
      "id": "8f11d955",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "9c0bae68",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data.T.shape"
      ],
      "id": "51488f4d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Matrix and vector operations\n"
      ],
      "id": "80b7422a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(1, 7).reshape(2, 3)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "f41db3e7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = np.arange(1, 7).reshape(3, 2)\n",
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "aaff83c6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(A, B)"
      ],
      "id": "0cb7bcdb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(B, A)"
      ],
      "id": "31cd3a20",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A @ B  # python 3.5 above"
      ],
      "id": "34dc115b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B @ A"
      ],
      "id": "33b83049",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "fbbc105e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "591d04f6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.arange(3)\n",
        "x"
      ],
      "id": "ce231b61",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(A, x)"
      ],
      "id": "52777c04",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A.dot(x)"
      ],
      "id": "dd3a3da3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A @ x"
      ],
      "id": "949cf5fe",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "7c70ae34"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.random.rand(3, 3)\n",
        "B = np.random.rand(3, 3)"
      ],
      "id": "9a13b9b6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ap = np.dot(B, np.dot(A, np.linalg.inv(B)))"
      ],
      "id": "d8400c7b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ap = B.dot(A.dot(np.linalg.inv(B)))"
      ],
      "id": "667ba9d3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B @ A @ np.linalg.inv(B)"
      ],
      "id": "a317f961",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "07b5bce6"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.inner(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "c31365da",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "e58a3cf2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "y = x[:, np.newaxis]\n",
        "y"
      ],
      "id": "742c8eb3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(y.T, y)"
      ],
      "id": "eaf9595c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "* Given two vectors, $\\mathbf{a} = [a_0, a_1, ..., a_M]~$ and $~\\mathbf{b} = [b_0, b_1, ..., b_N]$, $~$the outer product is $\\mathbf{a}^T\\mathbf{b}$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\\begin{pmatrix}\n",
        " a_0 b_0 & a_0b_1 & \\cdots & a_0 b_N \\\\\n",
        " a_1 b_0 & \\cdots & \\cdots & a_1 b_N \\\\\n",
        " \\vdots  & \\ddots &        & \\vdots  \\\\\n",
        " a_M b_0 &        & \\ddots & a_M b_N \\\\\n",
        " \\end{pmatrix}\n",
        "$$\n"
      ],
      "id": "38bd5b1a"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([1, 2, 3])"
      ],
      "id": "46b4e868",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.outer(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "bbf14fa4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "e2434d74",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(x[:, np.newaxis], x[np.newaxis, :])"
      ],
      "id": "966e2658",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(np.ones((2, 2)), np.identity(2))"
      ],
      "id": "808daf52",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(np.identity(2), np.ones((2, 2)))"
      ],
      "id": "0bc0e353",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "f9b3d66b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n",
        "y = np.array([5, 6, 7, 8])"
      ],
      "id": "2bc18cf3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.einsum(\"n,n\", x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "d7d870fd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.inner(x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "27f01734",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "B = A.T"
      ],
      "id": "276d4779",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.einsum(\"mk,kn\", A, B)"
      ],
      "id": "037d2aa0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.alltrue(np.einsum(\"mk,kn\", A, B) == np.dot(A, B))"
      ],
      "id": "ee8a2386",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    }
